25
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:18,228
-What?
-Yes. And I don't want it be. Believe me.

26
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:22,029
-But the universe has other plans for us.
-The universe is involved now.

27
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:24,316
