And you are. Great.

94
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,430
You know, there is
something I wanna ask you.

95
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,716
-Yeah?
-Yeah.

96
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,272
Are these too bling for our meeting?

97
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:28,552
