can get pretty weird.

100
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:39,916
And so I just have to say that if it ever
maybe gets to be too much for you--

101
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:44,432
Hey, broken record, I'm fine.
I just want us to kick ass on our pitch.

102
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:47,359
