104
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:53,877
-You guys ready to hit the road?
-Hey. Did you MapQuest the meeting?

105
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:57,038
-Yep. I got directions. Got snacks.
-I was gonna pack snacks.

106
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,639
