Mad Libs.

113
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:22,716
Those were my favorite
when I was a kid.

114
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:27,550
Well. I hope you'll be around
long enough to teach me how to play.

115
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,796
