to stop by for a visit.

122
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:48,197
-I think I've seen enough of him.
-Lindsay, why don't you go find...

123
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,920
-...the chauffeur and see if he'll pull up.
-Sure.

124
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,670
