you can make it up to her?

127
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:04,995
-Make things right with Ryan.
-What is it with my girls and that kid?

128
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,912
-Dad
-Fine. Fine.

129
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:10,951
