grown so close since I've been gone.

161
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:56,277
Well, Juju, Lindsay and l
are in the midst of some Mad Libs.

162
00:09:56,440 --> 00:10:00,115
-I'm sure you wanna go freshen up.
-Fine. I can take a hint.

163
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:04,353
Well, make yourself at home.
Caleb's casa es su casa.

164
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:07,199
