170
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:30,908
It's a Chanel clutch. Every girl I saw
in Paris was carrying one of these.

171
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:33,594
Thanks. You can leave it
on the dresser.

172
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:39,197
Marissa.

173
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,157
You know...

174
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:45,632
...when I was in Europe
I did some real soul-searching.

175
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:50,157
-I hope you didn't hurt yourself.
-I'm trying to talk to you.

176
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:53,477
-I know that you've been angry with me.
-What gives you that idea?

177
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:57,474
