180
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:10,438
-What if I took away your BlackBerry?
-Okay.

181
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:12,039
And your cell phone.

182
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:15,471
-You can't take away my cell phone.
-Oh, I think I just did.

183
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:18,797
You gonna throw the
bedroom furniture in the pool now?

184
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:22,396
