friends, so you're blackmailing me.

185
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:25,831
That's a great plan, Mom.
I'll see you at dinner.

186
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:57,600
-Not bad.
-Well, it beats living in my office.

187
00:11:57,760 --> 00:12:02,595
Your office was fine. It was the
running into Kirsten part that was rough.

188
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:04,034
