this morning.

190
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:10,551
I know I've complicated
your life lately.

191
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:14,030
And to thank you,
I got you a little Valentine's gift.

192
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:17,033
When I saw it, I couldn't resist.

193
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:23,594
Gandhi. Every time I see this...

194
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:27,150
...I think of you snoring
right next to me in that theater.

195
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:30,477
-I couldn't help it. It's a long movie.
-lt was our first date.

196
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:34,150
-lt was a lousy first-date movie.
-You're right.

197
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,914
Okay. I know that look.

198
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:44,675
-You wanna talk.
