Kirsten and me are bulletproof.

205
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,913
I don't wanna test that theory.

206
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:16,874
I should have seen this coming. One
thing I know about you, Sandy Cohen.

207
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:21,238
-You always do the right thing.
-I'll get you a list of the best lawyers.

208
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:23,478
You're gonna get through this.

209
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:26,518
I wish I was getting
through this with you.

210
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,953
Well.

211
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,115
Be careful what you wish for.

212
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,272
Hey there.

213
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:54,672
-How's your father doing?
-He's okay.

214
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:57,271
-And you?
-About the same.

215
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:01,031
The credit card company
called to verify...

216
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:03,794
...that you're staying at
the lnn at Playa del Rey.

217
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:07,953
It's for Rebecca. So she doesn't
have to stay at my office.

218
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:11,194
I know you're being put
in the middle of this.

219
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:14,352
But if you wanna take her case,
I'm not gonna stand in your way.

220
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:16,750
-I'm not gonna be her lawyer.
-Not because of me.

221
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:20,310
